---
title: Carb Smart Double Pork and Sweet Potato Salad with Creamy Herbed Sun-dried Tomato Dressing
description: A generous drizzle of creamy and herby sun-dried tomato dressing is the star of this recipe. Smoky pork is cooked and tossed with roasted sweet potatoes, tangy marinated radishes and a salad topper for a meal that only skimps on carbs, not flavour.
